 for YOU!</p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" id="e-1629380719828" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1629380719828"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1>WHat You'll do</h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1629380940691" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1629380940691"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p></p><!--StartFragment--><span style="font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Lt&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">✔️&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">Post about each month's Lift box on social media (unboxing videos preferred!)</span><br><!--StartFragment--><span style="font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Lt&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">✔️&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">Interact with our private Facebook group for subscribers. Community is everything to us.</span><br><!--StartFragment--><span style="font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Lt&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">✔️</span><!--EndFragment-->&nbsp;<span style="letter-spacing: 0px;">Participate in photoshoots and/or events when applicable (all costs covered).</span><br><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" id="e-1629380922339" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1629380922339"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1>WHat You'll get</h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1629380742932" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1629380742932"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><!--EndFragment--><p><span style="font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Lt&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0px;">✔️&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">If you're looking to earn a lot of money from this, this is not for you unfortunately. Payment is definitely a possibility but we're looking to grow a genuine community and not hire a bunch of random influencers who don't connect with the brand.</span><br><!--StartFragment--><span style="font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Lt&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">✔️&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">Free Lift Box every month.</span><br><!--StartFragment--><span style="font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Lt&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">✔️</span><!--EndFragment-->&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">Opportunity to make and be featured in Lift Box content (blog posts, photoshoots, events, etc).</span><br><!--StartFragment--><span style="font-family: &quot;Proxima Nova Lt&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">✔️</span><!--EndFragment-->&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">Opportunity to try and test products from Lift Box and partner brands. We get to do some really cool things!</span><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Row" class="gf_row" id="r-1629382160743" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1629382160743"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1629382160817" data-id="1629382160817"></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1629382160760" data-id="1629382160760"><div data-label="Liquid" data-key="liquid" id="m-1629381633044" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-liq